1. Got an error message "centos configure: error: Cannot find OpenSSL's <evp.h>" during installation pmpx
    solution: install openssl-devel by using "yum install openssl-devel"
  
2. Got an error message like "mcrypt not installed"...
    soultion: download libmcrpt from ftp://mcrypt.hellug.gr/pub/crypto/mcrypt/libmcrypt/ and compile it manually
